      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>creamy single soy</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] </span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> spinach </strong>to the pan and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook, covered, for 20-25 min or until the potatoes and squash have softened and the sauce has reduced – this is your <strong>winter</strong> <strong>squash & sage pie filling</strong></p>",
